{"tid":329061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好心啲人燒到40度就好去睇私家啦！","createTime":"2017-07-20T05:20:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-20T05:41:51.000Z","uid":34701,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4125f6fa2417b9a55586be065e085b3db205e878","tid":329061,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:20:28.000Z","msg":"然後仲要話人哋急症等得耐，咪就係因為大把人普通傷風感冒都走去排急症囉<br />\n但如果真係病到咁嚴重嘅我唔信佢睇一兩次私家診所嘅錢都攞唔出，又唔係過年冇得睇<br />\n條命定啲錢緊要啲呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利伸：純粹睇唔過眼，唔知咩心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a564ca3b15cc56388d2948dc85a18bbade86fa6","tid":329061,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:24:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a665d8d2a8eb785d48bb372b5003a6eb4072f029","tid":329061,"uid":50663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:29:35.000Z","msg":"又話辛苦 但寧願幾個鐘坐係醫院都唔啦啦聲睇私家返屋企訓"},{"pid":"1df1e76a2d5b92f2b28f2ab4e8aae42ecef21411","tid":329061,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:31:07.000Z","msg":"好多人唔係想濫用急症,而係普通門診要一早打電話BOOK定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f3d3437462f400eafd05a1bb482ccfa1611b450","tid":329061,"uid":37240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:32:34.000Z","msg":"凌晨點搵私家"},{"pid":"214b68b998b852a719bd8778284d96c2f961e582","tid":329061,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:33:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ffaffb54e6f791b75630b7af01c21a4b019ff1ce","tid":329061,"uid":6124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:33:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好多人唔係想濫用急症,而係普通門診要一早打電話BOOK定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n私家呢"},{"pid":"7cd25ceb518d0557f83a8337cc815c5964ccdd5b","tid":329061,"uid":90000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:33:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>凌晨點搵私家</blockquote><br />\n私家醫院"},{"pid":"ee330ec2d8c61f21a1c88c85b7af2e49e2f807dc","tid":329061,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:33:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d91f79423e463ecac80c8812a1fb9e82d3ac6983","tid":329061,"uid":45353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:33:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好多人唔係想濫用急症,而係普通門診要一早打電話BOOK定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成區得佢一間？<br />\n<br />\n又唔係專科<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n預約乜春"},{"pid":"5c550ff3b9e69045813083915f9cad176d4c4cdf","tid":329061,"uid":50663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:37:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>凌晨點搵私家</blockquote><br />\n而家點會冇夜診 我行落樓下都有一間"},{"pid":"6a06a0239ca77b72836b6cc0a554bcf7b2a2d7a1","tid":329061,"uid":54256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:37:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好多人唔係想濫用急症,而係普通門診要一早打電話BOOK定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成區得佢一間？<br />\n<br />\n又唔係專科<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n預約乜春</blockquote><br />\n其實你有冇用過普通科門診服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\n係要打電話去，佢比個時間你，岩就confirm 唔岩就行撚開<br />\n你打電話去係一定唔會有即日比你睇既時間，最快都1-2日後<br />\n利申:老人區，次次打去都2-3日後睇醫生，病到仆街既話真係你睇埋我果份"},{"pid":"c8402771f50d381b9ae6618c18d74157a5f08cb5","tid":329061,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:37:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你點知啲人過咗40度？</blockquote><br />\n琴日睇新聞講話有人係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7134b8ba45058fcb550347efb4845ff475df09d","tid":329061,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:39:56.000Z","msg":"啲錢緊要啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93ce785fe26e56dedfbe8ab89b62a510a7d03e6a","tid":329061,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:41:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>私家醫院定私家診所?<br />\n<br />\n樓主醫學知識好貧乏  發燒可以好多成因高燒一定係政府詳細好多<br />\n<br />\n就算知發燒原因好多私家診所都係做唔到野  <br />\n<br />\n你估得傷風感冒會發燒咩<br />\n<br />\n宜家D 90後以為發燒係好少事</blockquote><br />\n我知發燒有好多原因，但要等咁多個鐘就算本身小事都可以去到去嚴重啦<br />\n如果係我就一定唔會白白坐喺度等，你話凌晨時間難搵醫生，但就算自己嗰區冇，可能第區近啲嘅都有掛，病起上嚟就算要飛的都冇得講啦"}]}